headline: Big Returns In Surprising Places
summary: Looking back at stocks with a minimum of 20 years of returns, the study found that Nvidia had the greatest annualized compound return, which should surprise no one.

headline: Altria: It's Time To Return To This High Dividend Yield Opportunity (Rating Upgrade)
